## §14.1 Publication Minimum Dashboard

> Updated by publication-coach.md and 05_publication-pipeline.md after every publication session.

Batch year: YYYY
Option target: A / B / C (choose with guide)

### Option A Progress (3 Scopus/WoS/UGC + 1 conf)
- Journal 1: [ ] not-started
- Journal 2: [ ] not-started
- Journal 3: [ ] not-started
- Conference: [ ] not-started

### Option B Progress (2 Scopus/WoS/UGC + 1 granted patent + 1 conf)
- Journal 1: [ ] not-started
- Journal 2: [ ] not-started
- Patent: [ ] not-started (granted required — not just filed)
- Conference: [ ] not-started

### Option C Progress (2 Q1/Q2 + 1 conf)
- Q1/Q2 Journal 1: [ ] not-started
- Q1/Q2 Journal 2: [ ] not-started
- Conference: [ ] not-started

Engineering floor: ≥1 Q1/Q2/Q3 — [ ] not yet met

**At-submission check:** At least one publication must be ACTIVE (submitted / under review / accepted / published) at thesis submission time.

